In [[geometry]], the '''order-5 square tiling''' is a [[List_of_regular_polytopes#Hyperbolic_tilings|regular]] tiling of the [[Hyperbolic geometry|hyperbolic plane]]. It has [[Schläfli symbol]] of {4,5}.

== Related polyhedra and tiling ==
{{Order-5_regular_tilings}}

This tiling is topologically related as a part of sequence of regular polyhedra and tilings with vertex figure (4<sup>n</sup>).
