{{Order 5-4 tiling table}}

This hyperbolic tiling is related to a [[Infinite_skew_polyhedron#Semiregular_infinite_skew_polyhedra|semiregular infinite skew polyhedron]] with the same vertex figure in Euclidean 3-space.
